Test cases for the website - https://turbogames.io/game/aero
Test cases №1 -  №5 covers the bet placement functionality. Test cases №6 - Performance issue and №7 - UI issue

#1
Title: Verify the balance changes after placing a bet and losing
Type: Functional
Preconditions: Link to the game, starting balance 1000$
Steps to reproduce:
  1. Open the link
  2. Click on "Play now"
  3. Accept that user is over 18 years old
  4. Click on input field near first "Place bet" button
  5. Place 20$
  6. Click on "Ok" button
  7. Click on "Place bet"
  8. Lose the game
Expected result: The balance is 980$. Lost 20$
Status: Passed
Priority: High

#2
Title: Verify the balance changes after placing a bet and wining
Type: Functional
Preconditions: Link to the game, starting balance 100$
Steps to reproduce:
  1. Open the link
  2. Click on "Play now"
  3. Accept that user is over 18 years old
  4. Click on input field near first "Place bet" button
  5. Place 20$
  6. Click on "Ok" button
  7. Click on "Place bet"
  8. Click on "Cash out" button anytime is bigger the given bet amount
  8. Win the game
Expected result: The balance is 1007$. Won 27$
Status: Passed
Priority: High

#3
Title: Verify the maximum/minimum amount of bet
Type: Functional
Preconditions: Link to the game, balance at least 250$
Steps to reproduce:
  1. Open the link
  2. Click on "Play now"
  3. Accept that user is over 18 years old
  4. Click on input field near first "Place bet" button
  5. Place 200$
  6. Click on "Ok" button
  7. Observe the behavior
  8. Delete bet using keyboard
  9. Place negative bet (e.g., -2$)
  10. Observe the behavior
Expected result: Its not possible to put bet amount more then 100$ and less then 0.1$
Status: Passed
Priority: High

#4
Title: Verify bet amount changes: increase/decrease
Type: Functional
Preconditions: Link to the game, balance at least 100$
Steps to reproduce:
  1. Open the link
  2. Click on "Play now"
  3. Accept that user is over 18 years old
  4. Default bet amount 1$
5. Press "+" button till balance is 10$
6. Press "+" button till balance is 100$
7. Press "-" button till balance is 1$
8. Observe the behavior of "+","-" buttons
Expected result: If the bet amount is from 1$ to 9$, then the bet increases/decreases by 1$ each click. 
If the bet amount is from 10$ to 100%, then the bet amount increases/decreases by 10% each click
Priority: Low

#5
Title: Verify click on "Place bet", "Cancel" and "Cash out" buttons triggers corresponding sound 
Type: Functional
Preconditions: Link to the game, available sound output
Steps to reproduce:
  1. Open the link
  2. Click on "Play now"
  3. Accept that you are over 18 years old
  4. Click on "Place bet" button - bet placement sound plays
  5. Click on "Cancel" button - cancellation sound plays
  6. Click on "Cash out" button - plays the cash out sound
Expected result: Buttons "Place bet", "Cancel" and "Cash out" have separate audio feedback 
Status: Passed
Priority: Medium

#6
Title: Verify performance of the game
Type: Performance
Preconditions: Link to the game, opened DevTools, PC with stable internet and Google Chrome web v. 138.0.7204.97
Steps to reproduce:
  1. Open the link
  2. Click on "Play now"
  3. Accept that you are over 18 years old
  4. Open the DevTools
  5. In DevTools, open the Performance tab
  6. Start the recording by click on the play icon on upper left corner inside of DevTools
  7. Play the game for 20-30 sec
  8. Stop the recording
Expected result: No noticeable lag, frame and fps rate are stable
Status: Failed
Priority: High

#7
Title: Verify preview picture of the game is visible on mobile devices
Type: Visual/UI
Preconditions: Link to the game, iPhone 13 ProMax, Google Chrome mobile v.375.1.776343893 
Steps to reproduce:
  1. Open the link
  2. Observe the layouts of the game 
Expected result: Game preview is visible in a center of the page
Status: Failed
Priority: Medium
